intent.user_query: How do I retrieve the historical trend of AMP Worker Task utilization across the system using `resusagesawtV` view?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query for  on dbc: SELECT TheDate, TheTime, AVG(InuseMax) AS AverageAWTInUse FROM td_metric_svc.resusagesawtV GROUP BY TheDate, TheTime ORDER BY TheDate, TheTime;

arguments.sql: SELECT TheDate, TheTime, AVG(InuseMax) AS AverageAWTInUse FROM td_metric_svc.resusagesawtV GROUP BY TheDate, TheTime ORDER BY TheDate, TheTime;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
